{"tid":2023291,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[另類] [滅共預言] 中共係咪爆左條龍脈26 之 代馬龍巴開po","createTime":"2020-05-19T02:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T06:51:26.000Z","uid":276442,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"27b23cc26a893b0df926ad16d0f172ffac72d19f","tid":2023291,"uid":276442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:15:33.000Z","msg":"本討論不轉貼現代占星/網絡節目人仕預言<br />\n(因資料量大及凖確度不詳也尊重原創人仕之出處)<br />\n(古人已死另計)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">若各位自行轉貼請簡略及提供原出處</span><br />\n也請大家冷静思考，以免當局者迷<br />\n<br />\n本Post資料全沒科學根據，覺得岩睇睇落去，唔岩請回上一頁<br />\n舊帖重溫 (1-25) 請自行seach &quot;中共係咪爆左條龍脈XX&quot;<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於前post開始岀現物資及購買討論<br />\n以免過快爆Post物資討論及購買請移玉步至以下繼續<br />\n以作分流ㄧ&quot;常備有老佬箱/災難背囊&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1849767/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1849767/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">免責聲明 : 預言涉及風險，末日/混亂時期物資價格有時會大幅波動，價格可升亦可跌，胡亂購買更可變得毫無價值。 在作出成為末日能決定前，應仔細考慮物資 / 空間是否適合其財務狀況、目標和經驗、風險承受能力、以及其他有關情況，亦應了解投資物資所涉及的相關風險。 購買物資未必一定能夠安全，反而可能會招致損失。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9299e013c58fd00774b4a6269a173aac3bfc14f","tid":2023291,"uid":276442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a856a224ffdb7f1d9beeea81e952ccef590daa8","tid":2023291,"uid":276442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169d5de76f8a417b062a0d48bcb0a0ccdf68cfa5","tid":2023291,"uid":276442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T02:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b7fe7c9ceed